PrecisEnactment of the EVALUATION OF IMPAIRED OPERATION (DRUGS AND ALCOHOL) REGULATIONS which put in legislative terms Standard Field Sobriety Testing and the Drug Recognition Expert tests that have been performed by Canadian police officers for the past 10 years. These Regulations come into force on July 2, 2008.
